_sText:
“gg_no90_remix”

Blair (Bobpoblo) Burkhardt – Level Design
http://www.fpsbanana.com/members/776402

This is a remake of "gg_no90"
Shifty did the concept and level design.
Bobpoblo worked on additional lighting and details.

I remade this map because it was popular, but there were complaints of lag issues for some people.  I have removed the spot lights and added a new skybox texture to the map.  The removal of the spotlights has drastically increased the average FPS.  Enjoy!


Buy zones are included.
Please download, comment and enjoy!

- 64 Spawns
- Custom Skybox by komaokc
- Custom Textures by Ryan
- Cubemaps
- Optimized for better FPS
- Buy Zones
- Nav File
- Pakrat
